                                                                            <div class="article-head">
                                            <h1 class="article-headline">The Nationals are torturing their fan base with close losses</h1>
                                                                                            <h2 class="article-subline">Seven of the Nationals last eight playoff losses have come by one run</h2>
                                                                                                                                        


    <ul class="article-author row" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" section="author"><li class="headshot"> 
                                                    <a href="/writers/matt-snyder/" rel="author">
                                            <figure class=" img"><img class=" is-lazy-image" alt="    Matt Snyder
 mugshot" data-lazy="https://sportshub.cbsistatic.com/i/r/2016/05/04/69487861-f5f8-469b-b55a-c617fbddaec1/thumbnail/70x70/fe8d594fcde348aff1b9d391bfff363b/mattsnyder.png" src="" height="70" width="70"></figure></a>
                                            </li>
                                    
